aniers de 150$ ou plus</span><br>\n            <span class=\"free-shipping\"><strong>1-2 jours ouvrables</strong></span>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Prix fixe 65$<br>\n            <span class=\"free-shipping\">45$ pour les paniers de 200$ ou plus</span><br>\n            <span class=\"free-shipping\"><strong>2-4 jours ouvrables</strong></span>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"shipping-footer\">\n    <p>Notez que le ramassage en magasin sera toujours une option lors du paiement. Si vous constatez des irrégularités dans le calcul du coût de livraison, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter pour qu'on regarde ça ensemble.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  .shipping-grid-wrapper {\n    margin: 20px 0;\n    font-family: inherit;\n    color: #333;\n  }\n  .shipping-title {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .table-container {\n    overflow-x: auto;\n  }\n  .shipping-table {\n    width: 100%;\n    border-collapse: collapse;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;\n  }\n  .shipping-table th, .shipping-table td {\n    border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;\n    padding: 15px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .table-header-main {\n    background-color: #f9f9f9;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n  }\n  .row-label {\n    background-color: #fcfcfc;\n    text-align: left;\n    width: 30%;\n  }\n  .free-shipping {\n    display: block;\n    font-size: 0.9em;\n    color: #2c712c;\n    margin-top: 5px;\n  }\n  .disclaimer-cell {\n    font-style: italic;\n    font-size: 0.9em;\n    background-color: #fff9f0;\n  }\n  .shipping-footer {\n    font-size: 0.95em;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    border-left: 4px solid #ccc;\n    padding-left: 15px;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 600px) {\n    .shipping-table th, .shipping-table td {\n      padding: 10px;\n      font-size: 0.85em;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
